Medicaid API Endpoint Groups

Medicare API Endpoint Groups

Provider API Endpoint Groups

Create Groups of Endpoints

Usage

caid_group(x, call = caller_env(), ...)

care_group(x, call = caller_env(), ...)

pro_group(x, call = caller_env(), ...)

new_group(
  member_names,
  group_name = NULL,
  quick_call = FALSE,
  offset = 0,
  limit = 10
)

Arguments

x

<chr> endpoint alias

call

<env> environment to use for error reporting

...

Additional arguments passed to the group constructor

member_names

<chr> Alias representing the CMS data endpoint.

group_name

<chr> Name of the group.

quick_call

<lgl> call quick_() method on group if TRUE.

offset

<int> Offset for pagination.

limit

<int> Limit for pagination.

Value

S7 class_group object.
